data.description: 1 YEAR HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED. Spacious ranch home with an enormous screened in patio! Seller is ready to find a new homeowner. This fenced in homesite is amazing for enjoying wonderful family time, cook outs, holidays or quite mornings with a cup of coffee. Maybe you want to put a nice TV outside for game season. This is a 4-bedroom split ranch home with space for everything.  Just as you enter you will see a spacious dining room with built in shelves. You will enjoy all the new luxury Vinyl Tile making clean up easy. The great room has a vaulted ceiling with a wonderful spacious feel, and crown molding.  Large, mounted TV stays with the home. Kitchen features a raised breakfast bar, serving hatch so you can keep the Great room vibe going, lots of cabinet space, and room to move around. All appliances including the washer and dryer convey with the home. Perfect size breakfast room to mingle and hang out. 3 large bedrooms and a full bathroom with a double vanity are featured on the right side of your home giving you a little privacy from kids, guest or roommates. Walk into your large Owners space with room for a KING size bed, coffered ceiling and natural light! Large walk-in closet is featured in the Owners bathroom with a separate tub & shower, and double vanity. Close to SRP park, downtown, restaurants, I-20 and fun! Community Pool for fun summers. 1 Year home warranty included! Qualifies for 100% USDA financing.
